    <item>
      <title>在新一轮发行热潮中，黑石集团搁置 13 亿美元商业抵押贷款债券交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/blackstone-shelves-1-3-billion-cmbs-deal-amid-new-issue-frenzy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黑石公司原计划发行 12.75 亿美元商业房地产债券，但由于该债券的发行量持续飙升，该计划目前被搁置。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/blackstone-shelves-1-3-billion-cmbs-deal-amid-new-issue-frenzy</guid>
