    <item>
      <title>墨西哥央行称若比索波动率达到“极端水平”将介入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/banxico-says-it-can-step-in-if-peso-volatility-becomes-extreme</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥央行行长维多利亚·罗德里格斯表示，如果货币市场波动变得“极端”，墨西哥可能会采取干预措施恢复秩序。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/banxico-says-it-can-step-in-if-peso-volatility-becomes-extreme</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 21:23:48 GMT</pubDate>
