      <title>美联储决策日股市牛市创纪录：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管美联储的预期更为保守，但其并未改变华尔街对 2024 年利率将至少下降两次的押注，股市因此创下历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 22:44:58 GMT</pubDate>
